1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:59,120
Looks like fate is still on our side.
It didn't let us miss each other.

4
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:11,520
Commander.

5
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,600
What are you doing?

6
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,800
From now on,

7
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,880
I'll never let go of your hand again.

8
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,280
Do you really mean it?

9
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,600
Every word is sincere.

10
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:45,480
I swear it with all my heart.

11
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:52,240
(My little brother
really is lucky in love.)

12
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,840
(The cause he created back then)

13
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,240
(has now)

14
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:59,000
(become the result paving the way for me.)

15
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,800
(Shaoyuan,)

16
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,760
(this is what you owe me.)

17
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,840
Have some fruit and rest for a while.

18
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,320
Commander.

19
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:09,400
A letter from Lieutenant Cheng
has arrived.

20
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:20,920
(Gu Nianchi escaped. I killed him.
I was injured and will return after I recover. Cheng Yi)

21
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,320
How is it?

22
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,480
What did Cheng Yi say?

23
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,200
Cheng Yi said

24
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,000
he killed Gu Nianchi.

25
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,359
Are you sure?

26
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,680
This was written by Cheng Yi.

27
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,320
It's definitely him.

28
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:39,680
He never liked studying
when we were young.

29
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,880
I was the one who forced him
to practice writing for a few days.

30
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:44,200
He always liked to flick up
the last stroke of his characters.

31
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,360
Look at these.

32
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:47,880
This one.

33
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,320
This one too.

34
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,640
And this.

35
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:55,719
He also liked drawing a little orange
beside the character "Cheng."

36
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:57,800
(Cheng Yi)

37
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,800
If you're sure,

38
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,360
then it should be true.

39
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,440
This is...

40
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,640
Gu Nianchi's glasses.

41
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:27,920
Looks like

42
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,240
he really is dead.

43
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,120
What about Cheng Yi?

44
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,040
Did he say when he'll be back?

45
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,800
He said he was injured

46
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,159
and would return after recovering.

47
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,200
He told us not to worry.

48
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,360
He must be badly hurt.

49
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,880
His handwriting is all crooked.

50
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,280
It barely looks like his anymore.

51
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,400
That child...

52
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,760
Always trying to act tough.

53
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:06,440
Even when he's injured, he insists on
recovering before coming back.

54
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,720
Don't worry too much.

55
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:11,480
Since he doesn't want to return yet,
he's probably afraid you'll nag him.

56
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,160
Now that we've confirmed he's safe,

57
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,720
let's just wait for him to come back.

58
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,479
Now that I know Cheng Yi is safe,

59
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,600
I can finally stop worrying.

60
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:29,599
Next, it's time for me to meet
that Commander-in-Chief Li,

61
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,399
the one I once saved,

62
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:32,680
yet who now acts
without conscience or mercy.

63
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,600
My brother is leaving for another city.

64
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,280
I need to see him off at the station.

65
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,560
It's a shame I still haven't
dealt with Zhuang Yunqiu.

66
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,520
Otherwise, I'd be able to properly
visit my future brother in law.

67
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,240
Once I return
to my position as Commander,

68
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,320
we'll surely spend our lives together.

69
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,280
When that day comes,

70
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:59,680
I'll personally bring generous gifts
to thank the Xue family.

71
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,880
I believe in you.

72
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,240
And I'll do
everything I can to help you.

73
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,400
Darling.

74
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:07,400
Mm?

75
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:11,200
In the next few days,
I need to make a trip to Hengcheng.

76
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,440
Your injuries haven't even healed yet.

77
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:15,840
Why are you traveling so far?

78
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,600
I want to regain my position
as Commander as soon as possible.

79
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,720
Only then

80
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,240
can I protect you.

81
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,880
But right now,

82
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,480
I need some help from you.

83
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,440
Could you lend me some money?

84
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:38,040
Of course.
I'll give it to you when I get back.

85
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,640
I should get going now.

86
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,000
All right.

87
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,560
As instructed by you,

88
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,740
the letter has already been delivered
to the Commander's Residence.

89
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,520
The people sent out
by the Commander's Residence

90
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,700
to search have also been withdrawn.

91
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,120
Lu Shaoyuan...

92
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:23,920
Your soft heart will always
be your deadliest weakness.

93
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:29,080
I grew up with Cheng Yi too.

94
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:34,320
How could I not recognize
his handwriting?

95
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,479
The Xue family is wealthy and powerful.

96
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,320
We'll never have to worry
about money again.

97
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,360
That's right.

98
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,360
What's important isn't her.

99
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:51,280
It's everything the Xue family owns.

100
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:55,040
Sooner or later, it'll all belong to me.

101
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:57,320
With the Commander's charm,

102
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,920
I'm sure Miss Xue
will willingly fall for you.

103
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:09,240
(Golden Love Song)

104
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,280
Commander-in-Chief.

105
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:24,880
Long time no see.

106
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,920
Gu Nianchi.

107
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,200
So you still remember
I am your Commander-in-Chief.

108
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:34,800
I failed in my duty.

109
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:39,320
I've specially prepared a song for you,
Commander-in-Chief.

110
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:46,360
I don't think it's a matter
of failing your duty.

111
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,880
You're getting bolder and bolder.

112
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:51,200
You even dared touch my goods.

113
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,880
You've misunderstood me,
Commander-in-Chief.

114
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,320
Everything I've done

115
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,160
was for your sake.

116
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,320
Oh?

117
00:08:58,560 --> 00:08:59,800
For my sake?

118
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,040
Then I'd like to hear this.

119
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,519
You stole my goods

120
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,200
and cut off my source of income.

121
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,320
How exactly was that for me?

122
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,760
I've already found
the Zhuang family's daughter.

123
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:13,200
I promised her that as long
as she handed over the opium,

124
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,680
I would destroy it myself.

125
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,280
What?

126
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:19,240
You found the goods?

127
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:29,050
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

128
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:35,680
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

129
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:39,760
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

130
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:43,110
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

131
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:48,400
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

132
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:54,710
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

133
00:09:55,770 --> 00:10:01,370
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

134
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:05,290
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

135
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:08,489
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

136
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:13,629
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

137
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:17,949
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

138
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:20,529
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

139
00:10:20,530 --> 00:10:22,809
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

140
00:10:22,810 --> 00:10:26,359
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

141
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:30,889
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

142
00:10:30,890 --> 00:10:33,420
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

143
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,509
♪Still I walk into♪

144
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:39,109
♪The trap you set without regret♪

145
00:10:39,110 --> 00:10:43,159
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

146
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,739
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

147
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:47,899
♪A stand in can never cross♪

148
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:51,339
♪The shortest distance between us♪

149
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:56,310
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

150
00:10:56,470 --> 00:11:01,140
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

151
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,489
♪A substitute♪

152
00:11:05,490 --> 00:11:10,490
♪Needs no reason♪

